               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Headings and incipits of the texts; on the incipit page of each Gospel a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines); numbers of the “tituli”; chapter numbers and the word mǝʿǝraf; parts of the Canon tables; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
